(15, 1, '2018-07-08 11:01:41', '2018-07-08 11:01:41', '\n	<p>I need a Container</p>\n	<p>Delivered to</p>\n		<a href="#" target="_self"  role="button">\n						SEARCH\n		</a>\n	<p>Step 1: Select Material</p>\n<p>Pricing and disposal need vary depending on the materials placed in the container</p>\n	<p>Step 2: Select Container</p>\n<p>14-day rental period. Up to 6 Container sizes</p>\n	<p>Step 3: Delivery date</p>\n<p>Chose your delivery and pickup dates</p>\n		<a href="#" target="_self"  role="button">\n						l\n		</a>\n	<p>10 - 40 yard sizes</p>\n	<p>6 Container Sizes</p>\n		<a href="#" target="_self"  role="button">\n						See all Containers\n		</a>\n	<p>A standard rental period is 14 days</p>\n	<p>Dale’s Disposal provides 10, 20, 30 and 40 yd roll-off containers, 10 and 20 yard trailers and compactors to support the needs of contractors as well as residents in their efforts with construction, remodeling, demolishing or clean-up projects.</p>\n<p>Dale’s Disposal can also service industrial and commercial locations with permanent disposal service and has the flexibility to accommodate any pickup schedule.</p>\n	<p>Need Help Ordering?</p>\n	<p>Get placement instructions for your container to avoid any miscommunication</p>\n		<a href="#" target="_self"  role="button">\n						See FAQ\n		</a>\n	<p>Shipping</p>\n	<p>Shipping schedule<br />\nShipping rules</p>\n	<p><a href="#">Get Answers</a></p>\n	<p>Containers</p>\n	<p>Material Types<br />\nContainer Sizes</p>\n	<p><a href="#">Get Answers</a></p>\n	<p>Ordering</p>\n	<p>How ordering works<br />\nHow we weigh your container</p>\n	<p><a href="#">Get Answers</a></p>\n				<img src="http://dales.wemes.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/driver.png" alt="driver" itemprop="image" height="340" width="491" title="driver"  />\n	<p>Dale’s Disposal drivers</p>\n	<p>Our drivers have the experience to service your facility or residence and are conscious of their surroundings.</p>\n				<img src="http://dales.wemes.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/etroit.png" alt="etroit" itemprop="image" height="340" width="490" title="etroit"  />\n	<p>Serving Detroit since 2004</p>\n	<p>We take pride in providing prompt, efficient service to all of our customers, and look forward to continued growth in the tradition of Dale’s.</p>\n<p><a href="#"><strong>About Dales</strong></a></p>\n				<img src="http://dales.wemes.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/tricounty.png" alt="tricounty" itemprop="image" height="340" width="482" title="tricounty"  />\n	<p>Distribution Area</p>\n	<p>Dale’s Disposal provides full service dumpster rentals to the tri-county area of Macomb, Oakland and Wayne counties.</p>\n', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2018-07-11 06:04:01', '2018-07-11 06:04:01', '', 0, 'http://dales.wemes.com.ua/?page_id=15', 0, 'page', '', 0),
